{
  "texts": [
    "The idea is now to let ChatGPT generate such loop invariants.",
    "To this end, we need to tell ChatGPT what its task is.",
    "As briefly mentioned in the introduction, we expect ChatGPT to give loop invariants in the form of ACSL (ANSI C Specification Language [5]) assertions.",
    "ACSL is a specification language for C and offers a number of keywords for specifications in a design-by-contract style.",
    "Among others, there is the keyword loop invariant."
  ]
}